{"tid":180170,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"驚人跳槽！《復仇者聯盟》導演喬斯溫登將執導《蝙蝠女》獨立電影","createTime":"2017-03-30T18:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T14:49:30.000Z","uid":36167,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"446a22b6ba731f92dd8ee03720bfd11497180c4d","tid":180170,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:00:59.000Z","msg":"曾經執導過《復仇者聯盟》（The Avengers）、《復仇者聯盟：奧創紀元》（The Avengers: Age of Ultron）同時身為漫威電影宇宙前期重要領導者的喬斯溫登（Joss Whedon）有了新的主導計畫，不過這次他將策劃 DC 旗下的角色「蝙蝠女」！<br />\n<br />\n根據綜藝報的獨家報導，這位才華洋溢的編導將自製、自編、自導《蝙蝠女》獨立電影，目前尚未指出華納兄弟的高層以及 DC 擴充宇宙的傑夫強斯（Geoff Johns）是否會涉入，不過可以確定的是本片將會出現蝙蝠俠世界觀裡的其他角色。<br />\n<br />\n蝙蝠女是 DC 最知名的角色之一，卻從未有屬於自己的獨立電影，她首次出現於 1967 年，真實身份為芭芭拉高登，也就是高登局長的女兒，最近出現在動畫《蝙蝠俠：致命玩笑》（Batman: The Killing Joke）以及《樂高蝙蝠俠電影》。<br />\n<br />\n喬斯的跳槽將會是大英雄電影時代最驚人的新聞之一，他將會帶給 DC 什麼樣的衝擊？蝙蝠女會從哪一部 DC 擴充宇宙登場銜接，喬斯又會涉入整體規劃多深？都將會是之後大家非常好奇的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hypesphere.com/archives/87026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Farchives%2F87026&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8f85b1ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hypesphere.com/archives/87026</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://variety.com/2017/film/news/batgirl-movie-joss-whedon-warner-bros-1202018544/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2017%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fbatgirl-movie-joss-whedon-warner-bros-1202018544%2F&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=70f2039a\" target=\"_blank\">http://variety.com/2017/film/news/batgirl-movie-joss-whedon-warner-bros-1202018544/</a><br />\n<br />\n真係估你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲癲過KD轉會勇士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f68883aeec0a104f3b7764194ba3fea9ce9e03a","tid":180170,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"跳槽<img s